! Color Picker Plugin

Shows inline color swatches next to color values in the editor. Click a swatch to open a color picker.

!! Supported Color Formats

* Hex colors: `#fff`, `#ffffff`, `#ffffffaa`
* RGB: `rgb(255, 128, 0)`, `rgba(255, 128, 0, 0.5)`
* HSL: `hsl(120, 50%, 50%)`, `hsla(120, 50%, 50%, 0.5)`

!! Configuration

Enable/disable via Control Panel > Settings > CodeMirror > Editor > Color picker
